publish over ssh:
=====================
for publish over ssh
=>create a new job,
=>manage=>plugins=>available plugins=>search for publish over ssh =>install
next manage jenkins=>system=>publish over ssh=>ssh server=>in that add name=>tomcat-server
									Host-name=>IP address of tomcat
									username:ec2-user
							then check for password authentication=>
				in the key field copy pase the awskey of tomcat server=>save

=>navigate back to job =>configure=>post build actions=>add post build action=>send build ssh=>
				in the transfer=>source files: target/helloworld.war
					       =>remove prefix=>target
					       =>remove directory=>//opt//tomcat//webapps
=>apply and save
before building it =>in the tomcat run these two commands=>
$ sudo usermod -aG root ec2-user
$ sudo chmod -R g+w /opt/tomcat/webapps
